data.description: WELCOME to 807 Tropicana Blvd. This stunning, well kept, custom-built two-story home in the highly sought after East Bernard school district is sure to please on a Cul-de-sac street! Features include 4 generous sized bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms and a half bath! Enjoy the recently updated gourmet kitchen with sleek quartz countertops, recent paint, s/s appliances perfect for baking and cooking! Tons of space! Relax after a long day on the covered patio! Check out the giant back yard with a sparkling pool, perfect for outdoor fun and entertaining! How about a man cave or she shed, or gardening shed with a 16X12 Morgan building! Features also include a new roof and a new a/c! Don't miss this gem and schedule your showing today and make this your NEW home just in time for spring!!
